FBIS4-14644 "drsov064_t_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-064 Daily Report 4 Apr 1994 BALTIC STATES Estonia Eight-Ton Oil Leak Discovered at Russian Site Eight-Ton Oil Leak Discovered at Russian Site WS0404100194 Tallinn ETA in English 0710 GMT 4 Apr 94 WS0404100194 Tallinn ETA English BFN ["News Bulletin" No. 63/94] [Text] An estimated 8-ton oil leak was discovered in a Russian military site in Viimsi last week. The Russian military refused to provide access to the environment agencies, since the site has not yet been turned over to the Estonian authorities. The ministry claims that the fuel tanks are being used by a private oil company.
